PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1986-1/2914, which the Minister of Agriculture was authorized to make contributions to farmers in financial difficulty, payable to the FARM CREDIT CORPORATION, in amounts equal to concessions granted to farmers by the Farm Credit Corporation under arrangements made pursuant to the Farm Debt Review Act.
